4 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Section 26.1-01-03.3 of the North Dakota Century Code is
5 amended and reenacted as follows:
6 26.1-01-03.3. Penalty for violation of title.
7 Unless otherwise provided by law, a person who violates this title is subject, after hearing by
8 the commissioner, to payment of an administrative monetary penaltyfine of up to ten thousand
9 dollars for each violation. In addition to or in lieu of a monetary fine, the commissioner may
10 require restitution in the amount of direct financial loss be made to any person directly harmed
11 by a violation of this title.
